  </div>

  <!-- Legal footer note -->
  <div class="card" style="text-align:center;padding:28px;background:var(--surface2)">
    <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8">
      By accessing or using this software you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these terms.<br>
      For licensing inquiries or permission requests, contact the author directly via Discord.
    </div>
